animeTitle: Nissin Men-nashi Donbei x Himote House
animeDescription: A collaboration between Himote House and Nissin. Each episode begins with an introduction by the talking cat Enishi and is followed by an ad-libbed performance by a member of the Himote House promoting Nissin's line of soup cups that substitute noodles with tofu.
animeRelated: ['Other: Nissin no Donbei x Kemono Friends']
